        "description": "Help your patients prepare for their MRIs in under 5 minutes using space-age medical play. \n\nOur Virtual Reality Sim transforms the MRI experience into a magical mission, where patients team up with their co-pilot Veera, for a virtual voyage inside an MRI machine. \n\n*Interactive gameplay: Through fun challenges, patients learn the art of staying still, turning a crucial MRI requirement into an awesome game.\n\n*Sound familiarization: The mysterious symphony of MRI sounds becomes a familiar tune, as patients get acclimated to the unique noises they'll encounter.\n\n*Snug space: Our sim gently introduces the confines of an MRI tunnel, making the real experience less daunting.\n\n*Positive Affirmations: Every moment of courage is celebrated with virtual rewards, boosting their confidence and resilience.\n\n*Multiple languages: English and Spanish versions for inclusivity.\n\n*Scan Types: Prep patients for both brain and body scans.\n\nLet the Get Well Pals help you make MRIs easier and less stressful for everyone involved. ",
